
<style type="text/css">
  body{
    background-image: url(<%= asset_url('designersignup.jpg')%>);
    background-repeat: repeat-y;
    background-size: 100% 100%;
  }

  .designer-sign-up-caption{
    position: relative;
    top: 10vmin;
    background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    background-size: 100%;
    padding: 53px;
  }

  .designer-sign-up-caption p{
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 30px;
  }

  .designer-sign-up-caption p b{
    font-size: 24px;
  }

</style>

<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class=" col-md-6 ">
      <div class="designer-sign-up-caption">
        <p>
        Have you always find a platform to show your designs? You came to the right place that we provide a platform for interior designers to create their own profile and gallery. This will help you to get more new business. You can just focus on giving the best service to your client. We will lead more client who are interest in interior design here. Start to <b>create your profile NOW!</b></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class=" col-md-5 col-md-offset-1 ">
      <h2>Sign up</h2>

      <%= form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: registration_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
        <%= devise_error_messages! %>

        <div class="field">
          <%= f.label :email %><br />
          <%= f.email_field :email, autofocus: true %>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <%= f.label :password %>
          <% if @minimum_password_length %>
          <em>(<%= @minimum_password_length %> characters minimum)</em>
          <% end %><br />
          <%= f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "off" %>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <%= f.label :password_confirmation %><br />
          <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, autocomplete: "off" %>
        </div>

        <div class="actions">
          <%= f.submit "Sign up" %>
        </div>
      <% end %>

      <%= render "designers/shared/links" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>